{"tid":2447994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國新外交政策評估報告：俄羅斯是“頭號威脅”、中國是“競爭對手”","createTime":"2021-03-15T14:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T16:26:10.000Z","uid":391580,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e91b090c1b9feef6fd203e6b2356fe7dd3350793","tid":2447994,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:54:08.000Z","msg":"綜合英國星期日泰晤士報(The Sunday Times)最新消息，英國首相約翰遜將於當地時間3月16日公佈一份&ldquo;具有里程碑意義&rdquo;的安全、防務和外交政策綜合評估報告。星期日泰晤士報以此為題報導稱，&ldquo;英國新外交政策：俄羅斯是頭號威脅。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PduvbH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PduvbH.jpg&h=c1172fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，英國將宣布俄羅斯對英國構成最大威脅。原因可能與俄羅斯&ldquo;經常侵入英國水域和領空&rdquo;以及給俄羅斯貼上的&ldquo;隨時準備好在英國境內謀殺異見人士&rdquo;的標籤有關聯。此外，報導還援引這份報告稱，中國是英國的&ldquo;競爭對手&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;一個明顯的信號是，俄中兩國將被不同對待。&rdquo;《泰晤士報》援引消息人士的話說，&ldquo;俄羅斯是敵對國家，中國是全球挑戰。對中國的對策是：必要情況下建立競爭關係，可能的情況下建立合作關係，必要的時候予以反制&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯微信通訊社在一篇報導中指出，報告還提出，這份報告還提出增加軍費擴大網絡攻擊能力的計劃，以此反制莫斯科和北京方面。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府消息人士稱，&ldquo;對英國構成最大威脅的國家是俄羅斯。<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>報告沒有將中國列為威脅。中國是競爭對手</strong></span></span>，中國試圖竊取知識產權，在經濟安全方面構成威脅，但這無法和索爾茲伯里投毒案相比&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n星期日泰晤士報援引一名消息人士指出，俄羅斯是&ldquo;敵對國家&rdquo;，而中國是全球面臨的挑戰。他說：&ldquo;對於中國的對策是，必要情況下建立競爭關係，可能的情況下建立合作關係，必要的時候予以反制&rdquo; 。"},{"pid":"5e950df82e4a7effe2e36c45df861800a59617a4","tid":2447994,"uid":316927,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b892b20062a20c7e3cc712d2ba8ef645be5c992","tid":2447994,"uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pfD779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pfD779.jpg&h=a633dc7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b806a7166a3290a59a22afb0638cfefabc14c4c","tid":2447994,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b892b20062a20c7e3cc712d2ba8ef645be5c992","tid":2447994,"uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pfD779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pfD779.jpg&h=a633dc7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"佢究竟係學緊特朗普定點<br />\n<br />\n好難捉摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3170e8f4d978a7ed92ca0ffa36d2d272a99014","tid":2447994,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"英國跟美國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IkepNxJHVGs/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FIkepNxJHVGs%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=172789b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/mTv523QdaaY/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FmTv523QdaaY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=2e105f77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e57f3be4522ad4ea84836aace761ae71d032f8af","tid":2447994,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c3170e8f4d978a7ed92ca0ffa36d2d272a99014","tid":2447994,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"英國跟美國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IkepNxJHVGs/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FIkepNxJHVGs%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=172789b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/mTv523QdaaY/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FmTv523QdaaY%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=2e105f77&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"美國講咗好多次中國係頭號敵人喎<br />\n拜登都講咗好多次"},{"pid":"b8da48405914418a612486c033696930819a1009","tid":2447994,"uid":9542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"地緣政治係咁，對美國就係另一回事"},{"pid":"9e6d3e909337127f68fbbddd1a8acb2ce37acd04","tid":2447994,"uid":263143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"冇計啊 計算到地緣利益嘅時候，俄羅斯太近，中國太遠，尤其係美國目前全球影響力下降所以出此下策。日落國"},{"pid":"97d3ca6617d45aeaa6cd5812ce4e9f9f23313166","tid":2447994,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T16:26:10.000Z","msg":"屌你老母掉轉左啊仆街"}]}